data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat in Santa Maria! This 3-bed, 3-bath condo boasts 2280 sq ft of luxury living. The master bedroom on the lower floor ensures privacy and elegance.Stay comfortable year-round with central air conditioning and enjoy the convenience of indoor laundry. Step outside to a refreshing pool, clubhouse, and golf putting course - perfect for relaxation and entertainment.Nestled on the south end of Santa Maria, this condo offers a perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss the chance to make this your own! Contact us now for a private tour and experience the magic of Santa Maria living. Your dream home awaits - seize the moment!
